## Scoring Logic:

Score = (Availability * 50) + (Skill Match * 30)  + (Distance Score * 20)



## System Workflow:

[NGO Data] → [Database] → [Analysis + Priority]
                                ↓
                    [Matching Engine]
                                ↓
[Volunteers] → [Assignment] → [Execution → Feedback]



